I '''Ray Douglas Bradbury''' (Agosto 22, 1920 – Junio 5, 2012<!-- daughter stated death happened on Tuesday June 5; the story was subsequently reported on June 6)-->) metung yang Americanung talasulat king [[fantasy]], [[horror fiction|horror]], [[science fiction]], ampong [[mystery (fiction)|mysterio]] writer. Pekakilala ya king kayang nobelang [[dystopia]]n a ''[[Fahrenheit 451]]'' (1953), ampo reng kayang makuyad a salitang (short stories) science fiction mitipun king ''[[The Martian Chronicles]]'' (1950) ampo king ''[[The Illustrated Man]]'' (1951).  I Bradbury ing metung kareng pekasikat ampong matas kabilyan a talasulat a Americanu ning science fiction ampong aliwang uri ning [[speculative fiction]] anyang kadwang pulung siglu. Dakal kareng obra na ing miyalis king telebisyon ampong pelikula.

